title: 180: The Target Haul Episode (Fall '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode (Fall '22 Edition)
description:
In this episode, Lisa, Jamie & Mikey tried 15 foods, like confetti cake instant oatmeal, lentil mac & cheese bites, black bean hummus, salted butter caramel, cilantro-lime yogurt dressing, dill pickle cashews, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, the find of all finds: a Good & Gather Dip that’s a must have! Like really, you need to go and buy this now! No time to waste—push play, then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode.

P.S. Make sure you listen all the way through because Lisa is giving away signed issues of her new cookbook Simply Comfort!
itunes:summary: We hauled ourselves over to Target and found some GREAT finds this week on Chew The Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
